{"tid":1430132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報 22:06 警總爆發手足口病數警染病明","createTime":"2019-08-07T16:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T01:03:08.000Z","uid":275160,"like":636,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"09a7ae952191724d18446679c1abf6a41f96380a","tid":1430132,"uid":275160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"傳媒人潘小濤今早在facebook轉載警隊內部消息指出，「警察總部爆發手足口病」。警方向本報確認，警察總部於上月下旬有數名警務人員確診手足口病，衛生署表示，衛生防護中心暫未接獲有關呈報。根據法例，本港共有50種須呈報的傳染病，惟不包括手足口病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190807/s00001/1565186564787/%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%A3%E7%97%85%E6%95%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85-%E8%A1%9B%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E5%A0%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565186564787%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=f161f7e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565186564787%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1&h=ddbbed6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190807/s00001/1565186564787/%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%A3%E7%97%85%E6%95%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85-%E8%A1%9B%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E5%A0%